[Auction "S"]
2C pass 2D pass 2S pass 2NT pass 3H pass 4H pass pass pass
[Result ""]
{SOUTH has both Majors and enough points to open 2♣.

NORTH, with 4 points, responds with a negative 2

♦

.

SOUTH first bids her higher ranking suit, 2♠.

NORTH is too strong for second negative, he bids 2NT.

SOUTH now shows her second suit, 3

♥

.

NORTH is happy to bid the game in

♥

s.}
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 3, chOption: S, chBasis: N, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:2, nBasis: 0, nRot: 2, useStandardVul: true"]

