{pass

pass

SOUTH, with 9 points and a 5-card suit, should make a positive response, 2♠.

NORTH bids her

♥

s and SOUTH agrees the trump suit with a

4

♥

bid.

NORTH thinks there is a slam, so she invokes Blackwood. Hearing that SOUTH holds two Aces she bids

6NT. She could also have bid 6

♥

but 6NT scores a little more.}
